column1: #Text=The Washington Wizards defeated the Brooklyn Nets , 114 - 110 , at Barclays Center on Saturday evening .
#Text=The Wizards ( 31 - 21 ) have been mocked for some time for the " Trust the Process " slogan that has become associated with their run with the first - round win of the season .
#Text=Washington was able to withstand a late rally from the Nets ( 9 - 21 ) in the first half of a back - to - back set , building a 31 - 22 lead after one quarter .
#Text=However , the Wizards ( 31 - 44 ) regrouped at halftime and came out strong in the second quarter , outscoring the Nets by a 59 - 48 margin in the second half .
